args.prompt:
You have the text of actionable items from the email in variable <query_llm_3/>. For each action, output a JSON object suitable for calling the appropriate tool. Use the following format for each action, one per line:
- For creating a calendar event, output: {"tool":"create_calendar_event","args":{"title":"...","start_time":"YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM","end_time":"YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM","location":null,"participants":["email1","email2"]}}
- For sending an email, output: {"tool":"send_email","args":{"recipients":["..."],"subject":"...","body":"...","cc":null,"bcc":null,"attachments":null}}
- For adding participants, output: {"tool":"add_calendar_event_participants","args":{"event_id":"...","participants":["..."]}}
- For canceling an event, output: {"tool":"cancel_calendar_event","args":{"event_id":"..."}}
Do not include any other text. Just output the JSON lines.

